### GET all
GET http://localhost:5000/api/woods

### POST create
POST http://localhost:5000/api/woods
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teak Wood",
  "description": "Premium teak",
  "color": "Golden",
  "density": 720,
  "origin": "India",
  "pricePerUnit": 60.5,
  "available": true,
  "type": "hardwood"
}

### PUT update (replace :id)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/woods/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teak Wood 2",
  "description": "Updated"
}

### DELETE (replace :id)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/woods/1

